# 🐍 Snake Game

A classic snake game recreated using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** — playable directly in your browser. Eat the food, grow the snake, and avoid hitting the walls or yourself. Simple, fun, and nostalgic!

🎮 [Play the Game Live](https://cyberbot-ux.github.io/Snake-game/)

---

