---

## 🎯 Game Rules

- Use arrow keys to control the snake:
  - `↑` Up
  - `↓` Down
  - `←` Left
  - `→` Right
- Each time the snake eats food, it:
  - Grows longer
  - Score increases
- The game ends if the snake:
  - Hits the wall
  - Collides with itself

---

## ✨ Features

- Smooth animations and grid-based movement
- Dynamic food placement
- Score tracking
- Game over detection
- Simple, responsive design

